    Convert a list to a kpilist

    as.kpilist.Rd

    Convert a list to a kpilist

    as.kpilist(x)

    Arguments

    x

    list of kpi objects

    Value

    a kpilist

    Examples

    l <- lapply(c("drat", "hp", "qsec"), function(x){
 kpi(mtcars,
     var = x,
     by = c("am", "cyl"),
     kpi_fn = kpi_fn_median)
})
as.kpilist(l)
